@host = http://localhost:3000

### 1) Tạo promotion (ADMIN)
POST {{host}}/promotions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WELCOME10",
  "type": "PERCENT",
  "value": 10,
  "validFrom": null,
  "validTo": null,
  "minNights": 1,
  "minTotal": 0,
  "usageLimit": 2,
  "isActive": true
}

### 2) Danh sách promotions
GET {{host}}/promotions

### 3) Lấy promotion theo code
GET {{host}}/promotions/by-code/WELCOME10

### 4) Preview (không giữ slot)
# Đổi {{bookingId}} cho đúng
GET {{host}}/promotions/preview?bookingId={{bookingId}}&code=WELCOME10

### 5) Apply on HOLD/REVIEW
POST {{host}}/promotions/apply-on-hold
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "code": "WELCOME10"
}

### 6) Confirm on PAID (first-paid-wins; không vượt quota)
POST {{host}}/promotions/confirm-on-paid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}"
}

### 7) Release khi CANCELLED/EXPIRED/REFUNDED
POST {{host}}/promotions/release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "decreaseUsage": true,
  "cause": "REFUNDED"
}
